/0000-0003-1322-8680</a></span>, <span property="author" typeof="Person" role="listitem"><a href="#con9"><span property="givenName">Alessandro</span> <span property="familyName">Furlan</span>, <span property="honorificSuffix">MD</span></a> <a class="orcid-id" href="https://orcid.org/0000-0002-6099-1323" property="identifier" aria-label="ORCID identifier" target="_blank">https://orcid.org/0000-0002-6099-1323</a></span>, and <span property="author" typeof="Person" role="listitem"><a href="#con10"><span property="givenName">Frank H.</span> <span property="familyName">Miller</span>, <span property="honorificSuffix">MD</span></a> <a class="orcid-id" href="https://orcid.org/0000-0001-9506-9411" property="identifier" aria-label="ORCID identifier" target="_blank">https://orcid.org/0000-0001-9506-9411</a></span></span></span><a href="#tab-contributors" class="to-authors-affiliations" data-id="article-authors-viewall">Authors Info &amp; Affiliations</a></div><div class="core-self-citation"><div property="isPartOf" typeof="Periodical"><span class="heading">Publication</span>: <span property="name">RadioGraphics</span></div><div class="core-enumeration"><span property="isPartOf" typeof="PublicationVolume">Volume <span property="volumeNumber">45</span></span><span class="delimiter">, </span><span property="isPartOf" typeof="PublicationIssue">Number <span property="issueNumber">9</span></span></div><div class="doi"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1148/rg.240210" property="sameAs">https://doi.org/10.1148/rg.240210</a></div></div><div class="info-panel"><div class="info-panel__left-content"><div class="info-panel__cme info-panel__item"><a href="/servlet/linkout?doi=10.1148%2Frg.240210&suffix=s0&url=https://api3.rsna.org/lms/v1/sendToJournalCMETest?doi=10.1148%2Frg.240210" class="btn btn--cme" data-toggle="tooltip"><i aria-hidden="true" class="icon-checkmark2"></i><span class="link-text">CME</span></a></div><div class="info-panel__metrics info-panel__item"></div></div><div class="info-p