&amp;author=Y+Karagoz&amp;author=B+Kesici&amp;publication_year=2013&amp;journal=ISRN+Hematol&amp;pages=673781&amp;pmid=24159391">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">6.</div><div id="r6" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Gioia S, Nardelli S, Ridola L, Riggio O. Causes and management of non-cirrhotic portal hypertension. <em>Curr Gastroenterol Rep</em> 2020;22(12):56.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1007/s11894-020-00792-0">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/32940785/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Causes+and+management+of+non-cirrhotic+portal+hypertension&amp;author=S+Gioia&amp;author=S+Nardelli&amp;author=L+Ridola&amp;author=O+Riggio&amp;publication_year=2020&amp;journal=Curr+Gastroenterol+Rep&amp;pages=56&amp;doi=10.1007%2Fs11894-020-00792-0&amp;pmid=32940785">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">7.</div><div id="r7" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Rajekar H, Vasishta RK, Chawla YK, Dhiman RK. Noncirrhotic portal hypertension. <em>J Clin Exp Hepatol</em> 2011;1(2):94–108.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1016/S0973-6883(11)60128-X">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/25755321/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Noncirrhotic+portal+hypertension&amp;author=H+Rajekar&amp;author=RK+Vasishta&amp;author=YK+Chawla&amp;author=RK+Dhiman&amp;publication_year=2011&amp;journal=J+Clin+Exp+Hepatol&amp;pages=94-108&amp;doi=10.1016%2FS0973-6883%2811%2960128-X&amp;pmid=25755321">Google Scho